 -------------------------------------------------------------------------------
           LegSem LegStar Eclipse plugins Version 1.2.0
                           Release Notes
 -------------------------------------------------------------------------------

PREREQUISITES:

 LegStar Eclipse plugins require Eclipse version 3.2.1 and above.
 
INSTALLING/UNINSTALLING:

  [[1]] Within Eclipse, create a remote site using:
 
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  Help-->Software Updates-->Find and Install-->Search for new features-->New Remote site
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  
  Have the URL point to http://www.legsem.com/legstar/eclipse/update and select all the
    features.

 [[2]] Restart Eclipse and check that the LegStar plugins show up in:
 
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  Help-->About Eclipse SDK-->Plug-in details
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   
 [[3]] To uninstall, use:

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  Help-->Software Updates-->Manage Configurations.
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

  then right-click on the feature you wish to uninstall.

DOCUMENTATION:

 Documentation available at http://www.legsem.com/legstar/legstar-common-plugin

